## Updating a Resource Folder

```shell
curl -XPUT "<%= api_url %>/api/zones/5/folders/50" \
  -H "Authorization: BEARER <%= curl_token %>" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"folder":{
    "active": true,
    "visibility": "private",
    "tenantPermissions": {
      "accounts": [1]
    },
    "resourcePermissions": {
      "all": false,
      "sites": [
        {"id": 1}, {"id": 2}, {"id": 3}
      ]
    }
  }}'
```

